# Components Directory

Place custom Vue components here for reuse across slides.

## Example Usage

Create a component:

```vue
<!-- Counter.vue -->
<script setup>
import { ref } from 'vue'
const count = ref(0)
</script>

<template>
  <button @click="count++">
    Count: {{ count }}
  </button>
</template>
```

Use in slides.md:

```markdown
---
<Counter />
---
```

## Tips

- Extract complex slide layouts into components
- Create reusable visualization components
- Share components between presentations by symlinking
